description: Set of 3 makeup cases, various sizes, all in clear plastic. Silver frames. Silver hardware. Clear plastic faces. Large and medium case have locks and come with keys. Large and medium case have mirrors on the inside of lid. Small case 4.75 inches x 3 inches x 3 inches 7.6 ounces medium case 6 inches x 4.5 inches x 4.5 inches 13.2 ounces large case 7.25 inches x 5.25 inches x 5.25 inches cases fit one inside the other for easy storage when not in use. All 3 items come with Shany cosmetics logo on their top.
title: SHANY Cosmetics 3 In 1 Makeup Case Clear Nail Art Organizer and Case Makeup Organizer Set of 3, 3 Count
